CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 28, 1960, pg. A5, reads: "Checking Ballot - Looking over the list of names for the 'Outstanding Allegheny County High School Athlete' award are Judy Hopson, Junior Courier reporter, center, and hopefuls like Mike Biscegila, left and Verner Rusell [Russell?], right, of Westinghouse High School. The winner will be announced at The Courier - WAMO Home-A-Rama.  The award will be presented by Althea Gibson.  You can help your choice win by checking his name on the ballot presented in sports section of The Courier. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mike Biscegila, Judy Hopson holding newspaper, and Verner Russell, standing in interior
